Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:23.10,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走出黑暗 重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:26.18,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直至光芒 照亮结局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:29.98,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}丑恶嘴脸 咒骂不止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.31,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我的最后一战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:40.03,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:46.79,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童绞尽脑汁 只为保护手中硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:53.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恶魔脸孔之下 一副天使面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:04:00.30,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩童手中 紧攥最后一枚硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.26,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毁灭与重生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:06.51,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才是真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.11,op-en,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:23.10,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's start a new life from the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:26.18,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Until the light reveals the end
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:29.98,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sinister faces, growing curses
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.31,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is my last war
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:40.03,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels playing disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:46.79,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling to their coins squeezing out their wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:53.29,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Angels planning disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:04:00.30,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Children cling on to their very last coins
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.26,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Destruction and regeneration
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:06.51,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You are the real enemy
